                    <h2>ABOUT</h2>

<p>The UC Irvine (UCI) branch of the UCLA-UCI Alpha Stem Cell Clinic (ASCC) provides a centralized infrastructure from which to work with UCI faculty and staff to enhance stem cell clinical research and activities at UCI. The UCI branch of the UCLA-UCI Alpha Stem Cell Clinic:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Is part of the California Institute for Regenerative Medicine (CIRM) Alpha Stem Cell Clinic network</li>
	<li>Promotes and facilitates scientific collaborations and interactions</li>
	<li>Provides centralized clinical research infrastructure support</li>
	<li>Accelerates the implementation of clinical research trials</li>
</ul>
CIRM Alpha Stem Cell Clinics: <a href="pdfs/Cell-Stem-Cell-Alpha-Clinics-Article-2018.pdf" target="new">Collaboratively Addressing Regenerative Medicine Challenges &#160;&#187</a>                 
                
                    
